{
  "groups": [
    {
      "end": 15.47,
      "id": "p0",
      "index": 0,
      "section_index": 0,
      "section_kind": "weather_opening",
      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 9.77,
      "text": "It is currently a clear morning in Berlin-Tempelhof with a temperature of 29 degrees Celsius."
    },
    {
      "end": 19.21,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 16.51,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a886da6c593"
      ],
      "end": 38.25,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 19.65,
      "text": "Hugging Face has simplified how developers deploy large language models. Users can now launch private, OpenAI-compatible endpoints using vLLM with a single command. This removes the need for manual server management when moving from experimentation to active hosting."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a89768a9342"
      ],
      "end": 62.7,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 38.84,
      "text": "While software tools simplify deployment, NVIDIA is focusing on the underlying hardware efficiency. The company is streamlining how shaders access data through end-to-end support for Vulkan descriptor heaps. This optimization of resource binding improves performance for rendering and AI workloads that require efficient memory access."
    },
    {
      "end": 65.82,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 62.7,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 73.84,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 65.82,
      "text": "This afternoon will remain clear with temperatures between 29 and 39 degrees Celsius and rain chances up to 10 percent."
    },
    {
      "end": 76.46,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 73.84,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 84.5,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 76.9,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 85.0,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 84.5,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
